column5: Juli and I got out with her dad and brother, Scott, for an afternoon of beautiful weather and a couple of take home beauties.  Couldn't have asked for more beautiful weather. Couple of photos...      First fish we've ever kept from this spot, but, it's been awhile since a fresh fish dinner.  Hope everyone had as much fun on opening day as we did!
Nothing better than catching a few esp on opener, and having a great day with the family.
Wow, they really are pretty  Awesome!!!
Awesome bows buddy!  Wha'd they fall victim to?  Congrats to you guys for getting out!  Next time you're in my neck of the woods you better pop in for a beer!
Ataboy Frankie Beauties Are one of those an upgrade?
Beauty Bows Sounds like you had a great time.I bet they tasted great too
